Conference in Memory of Aurelio Carboni - First Announcement.

Herewith we announce the Conference in Memory of Aurelio Carboni, that will=
  be held in Milano, June 24 - 26 2013, at the Department of Mathematics "Fe=
derigo Enriques" (Universit=C3=A0 degli Studi).

